    <h1>About VEX Squad</h1>
    <p>VEX Squad is a Fortnite-focused gaming community created by me and my friend to bring together gamers who love competing and having fun.</p>
    <p>Since 2025, we've grown into a tight-knit squad that values teamwork, positivity, and building each other up in and out of the game. We focus on Fortnite but also enjoy branching out to other exciting and sometimes crazy games.</p>
    <p>Whether you want to improve your skills, watch awesome streams, or just chill with friendly players, VEX Squad is the place for you. Our community is all about support, sharing tips, and creating memorable gaming moments together.</p>
    <p>Join us and be part of a squad that plays hard, laughs hard, and wins together!</p>
