    <h1>What We Do</h1>
    <p>At VEX Squad, Fortnite is our main battlefield. We spend hours dropping into the island, building crazy forts, and battling it out to secure those Victory Royales. Whether you’re mastering your builds, honing your aim, or strategizing with the squad, Fortnite is where we shine.</p>
    <p>But we don’t stop there — we also love to mix things up with some wild and crazy games! From fun party games to unexpected indie hits, our squad enjoys exploring new games that bring laughter, chaos, and fresh challenges.</p>
    <p>We regularly organize game nights, tournaments, and community events that give everyone a chance to compete, collaborate, and just have a blast. Whether you’re in for the serious Fortnite grind or the fun of unpredictable games, VEX Squad has something for you.</p>
    <p>Want to join the fun? Hop on our Discord or check out our YouTube channel to see what we’re up to!</p>
